* {{ill|Tatsuya Yoshimura|ja|吉村達也|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tatsuya Yoshimura|qq=}} - A novelist who wrote ''Kyoto Tenshitsukinuke-dōri no Koi'' (Kyoto's Love on Tenshitsukinuke Street).
* {{ill|Masashi Yamada (director)|ja|山田雅史|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Masashi Yamada (director)|qq=}} - A film director who produced ''Tenshitsukinuke Rokuchōme.''

